<div class="container" id="fx-liquidity">
    <div class="fx-section">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm">
                <h1 class="main-title">[% l('Multi-asset liquidity solutions') %]</h1>
                <p>[% l('ChampionFX provides MT4/MT5 brokers, institutional clients, and crypto exchanges with top-tier liquidity solutions on a wide range of assets.') %]</p>
                <p>[% l('Access market quotes and trade execution on major currency pairs, spot metals, CFD indices, popular cryptocurrencies, and more.') %]</p>
                <p>[% l('Our liquidity solutions are ideal for brokers who lack access to direct prime brokerage relationships with a top-tier bank due to the size of their balance sheet.') %]</p>
                <p>[% l('Our commitment to integrity and reliability means that we always strive to give you access to the best pricing and liquidity possible') %]</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row center-text box-grid box-grid-align-start">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <h2>[% l('Key features') %]</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="box fill-bg-color">
                    <span class="fx fx-multi-asset-execution"></span>
                    <p class="text-bold">[% l('Multi-asset execution') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('Over 50 FX pairs, plus spot metals, CFD indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="box fill-bg-color">
                    <span class="fx fx-liquidity-solution"></span>
                    <p class="text-bold">[% l('Top-tier liquidity') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('Access market quotes and trade execution from top-tier liquidity providers, including banks and non-banks.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="box fill-bg-color">
                    <span class="fx fx-full-transparency"></span>
                    <p class="text-bold">[% l('Full transparency') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('Subscribe to ChampionFX liquidity and see the exact liquidity venues we are streaming from via the ‘Bank’ column in your MT5 platform.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="box fill-bg-color">
                    <span class="fx fx-backoffice-support"></span>
                    <p class="text-bold">[% l('Back-office support') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('Receive back-office support for post-trade risk management and real-time trade/position monitoring.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="separator fill-bg-color"></div>

        <div class="row center-text box-grid">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <h2>[% l('How it works') %]</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 push-md-2 col-lg-4 push-lg-0">
                <div class="box box-bordered">
                    <span class="fx fx-one-zero"></span>
                    <p class="box-title">[% l('One Zero') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('MT4 and MT5 brokers can connect directly to our liquidity on the One Zero bridge by using built-in plugins.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 push-md-2 col-lg-4 push-lg-0">
                <div class="box box-bordered">
                    <span class="fx fx-mt5-gateaway"></span>
                    <p class="box-title">[% l('MT5 Gateaway') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('MT5 also provides native gateway connectivity to our liquidity that you can configure to meet your specific requirements.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 push-md-2 col-lg-4 push-lg-0">
                <div class="box box-bordered">
                    <span class="fx fx-fix-api"></span>
                    <p class="box-title">[% l('Fix API') %]</p>
                    <p>[% l('Everyone else can use the FIX API to connect to our One Zero bridge &mdash; subject to a conformance test.') %]</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="separator fill-bg-color"></div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <h2>[% l('Highlights') %]</h2>
                <ul class="bullet">
                    <li>[% l('Access to multi-asset liquidity and back-office functionality via margin accounts') %]</li>
                    <li>[% l('Super-tight spreads with zero commission and no minimum volume requirements') %]</li>
                    <li>[% l('Access to STP trading conditions') %]</li>
                    <li>[% l('We can accomomodate our liquidity solutions to the requirements of offshore MT4/MT5 brokers') %]</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10 push-md-1">
                <div class="box center-text fill-bg-color">
                    <span>[% l('Interested in our liquidity solutions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:partners@champion-fx.com">partners@champion-fx.com</a> for more info.') %]</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>